  "texts": [
    "The right panels show our model predictions for simultaneous stimulation (for sequential simulation, see Supplementary Videos (LettersEstimatedLocation.mov-Supplementary Video 5, LettersPatientLocation.mov-Supplementary Video 6) for Fig. 6).",
    "Panel for Fig. 8) for three electrode array configurations.",
    "The number of electrodes were chosen to be roughly similar across arrays, while compensating for slight differences in the area of visual field represented.",
    "Figure 8A shows electrodes arranged to produce a regular tiling in visual space.",
    "This array clearly underrepresents the fovea -producing a sparse collection of tiny phosphenes in the fovea."
